<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:718.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">這個句型是人物</span><span class="cls_013">2</span><span class="cls_008">對人物</span><span class="cls_013">1</span><span class="cls_008">進行的動作</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_008">從受動人物</span><span class="cls_013">1</span><span class="cls_008">的立場敘述的句型。用被動動</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:738.54px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">詞的被動句的主題是人物</span><span class="cls_013">1</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_008">施動者</span><span class="cls_009">（</span><span class="cls_008">人物</span><span class="cls_013">2</span><span class="cls_009">）</span><span class="cls_008">用助詞に</span></div>
