<div style="position:absolute;left:201.60px;top:388.14px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">じ  てん  しゃ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:262.80px;top:388.14px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">しゅう  り</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:391.74px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">⑥</span><span class="cls_006">わたしは</span><span class="cls_007">   </span><span class="cls_006">友達に</span><span class="cls_007">   </span><span class="cls_006">自転車を</span><span class="cls_007">   </span><span class="cls_006">修理して</span><span class="cls_012">  </span><span class="cls_006">もらいました。</span></div>
