<div style="position:absolute;left:25.20px;top:473.34px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">４</span><span class="cls_007">.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:473.40px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">名詞</span><span class="cls_003">（</span><span class="cls_002">物</span><span class="cls_003">／</span><span class="cls_002">事</span><span class="cls_003">）</span><span class="cls_012">    </span><span class="cls_006">が</span><span class="cls_012">／</span><span class="cls_006">は</span><span class="cls_012">  </span><span class="cls_002">被動動詞</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:493.74px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">敘述某件事情時</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_008">如果不把重點放在行為者身上</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_008">就可以把物或事作為主語</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_008">用</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:514.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">被動動詞來表達。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:157.20px;top:530.94px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">むかし</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:201.60px;top:530.94px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">に  ほん</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:254.40px;top:530.94px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">え</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:291.60px;top:530.94px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">はっ  けん</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:534.54px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">⑦</span><span class="cls_006">フランスで</span><span class="cls_007">   </span><span class="cls_006">昔の</span><span class="cls_007">   </span><span class="cls_006">日本の</span><span class="cls_007">   </span><span class="cls_006">絵が</span><span class="cls_007">   </span><span class="cls_006">発見されました。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:78.00px;top:556.80px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">在法國發現了日本古代的繪畫。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:82.80px;top:571.74px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">に  ほん</span></div>
