<div style="position:absolute;left:507.30px;top:0.00px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">課</span><span class="cls_005">:37 (</span><span class="cls_004">頁</span><span class="cls_005">:10/10)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:25.20px;top:0.00px" class="cls_003"><span class="cls_003">６</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_002">名詞</span><span class="cls_012"> </span><span class="cls_006">から</span><span class="cls_003">／</span><span class="cls_002">名詞</span><span class="cls_012"> </span><span class="cls_006">で</span><span class="cls_012">  </span><span class="cls_006">つくります</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:51.60px;top:19.74px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">製造東西時</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_008">原料用「から」</span><span class="cls_009">，</span><span class="cls_008">材料用「で」表示。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:146.40px;top:36.54px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">むぎ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:199.20px;top:36.54px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">つく</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:40.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">⑫</span><span class="cls_006">ビールは</span><span class="cls_007">   </span><span class="cls_006">麦から</span><span class="cls_007">   </span><span class="cls_006">造られます。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:78.00px;top:62.40px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">啤酒是用麥子釀造的。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:78.00px;top:77.34px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">むかし</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:109.20px;top:77.34px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">に  ほん</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:159.60px;top:77.34px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">いえ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:201.60px;top:77.34px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">き</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:238.80px;top:77.34px" class="cls_010"><span class="cls_010">つく</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:80.94px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">⑬</span><span class="cls_006">昔</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_006">日本の</span><span class="cls_007">   </span><span class="cls_006">家は</span><span class="cls_007">   </span><span class="cls_006">木で</span><span class="cls_007">   </span><span class="cls_006">造られました。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:78.00px;top:103.20px" class="cls_002"><span class="cls_002">古代日本的房子是用木材建造的。</span></div>
